VoiceDir9.137EC4: Somber. Hopes they will find their way.
Line9.137EC4: They tell us of others who wander without a tribe. As for their fate... only the ancestors know.
VoiceDir7.137EC4: Looking around at her people. Proud.
Line7.137EC4: Not all you see here were born of the Oxen Tribe. Some found us as you did... guided by fate.
